sequenceDiagram
    participant Player
    participant Controller as Minigame Controller
    participant Flow as SessionFlow<TState>
    participant UI as ModeMenu/Pause/Completion UI

    Player->>UI: Select difficulty + mode
    UI->>Controller: StartGame(config)
    Controller->>Flow: Register(states)
    Controller->>Flow: TransitionTo(Menu/Countdown)

    loop Every frame
        Controller->>Flow: Tick()
        Flow-->>Controller: onTick callback for current state
    end

    Controller->>Flow: TransitionTo(Playing)
    Note over Controller,Flow: Gameplay events update score/timer/streak

    alt Target score reached or rounds complete
        Controller->>Flow: TransitionTo(Complete)
        Controller->>UI: Show completion panel
        Player->>UI: Quit
        UI->>Controller: ReturnToMinigamesMenu()
    else Player pauses/restarts
        Player->>UI: Pause
        UI->>Controller: Pause/Resume/Restart
    end
